{"tid":2104442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李予信：中共怕民意結集","createTime":"2020-07-12T03:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T06:42:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6af13b28bde2d2470bf0945e70e851e8227e8d55","tid":2104442,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200712/ASPW2I3V5VKFNLELQAIBLWZKJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2FASPW2I3V5VKFNLELQAIBLWZKJY%2F&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=fd266d57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2FASPW2I3V5VKFNLELQAIBLWZKJY%2F&h=b399fcfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200712/ASPW2I3V5VKFNLELQAIBLWZKJY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李予信：中共怕民意結集<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a-z2X37tlJkovbl4V7Wms54hzyk=/609x531/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/STWORP3G5MGX6UVQH634JQY4TE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa-z2X37tlJkovbl4V7Wms54hzyk%3D%2F609x531%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSTWORP3G5MGX6UVQH634JQY4TE.gif&h=6cb3b08b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公民黨李予信昨獲前黨魁余若薇等人支持。<br />\n<br />\n【超區<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派在現屆超級區議會中佔三席，來屆希望再搶多一席，今次初選會由五隊中挑選四隊出線。2016年立會選舉以49萬票當選的民主黨鄺俊宇到各區呼籲巿民支持初選，傍晚於銅鑼灣東角道與黨友許智峯一同嗌咪，<br />\n.................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉：曾國衞恐嚇令人反感<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警查票站影市民 製白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n公民黨今屆由東區區議員李予信出戰超區，昨晚尾站落腳銅鑼灣拉票，李指中共怕民意結集，「返到嚟銅鑼灣就係想提醒香港人，我哋團結先有希望。」前學聯岑敖暉稱投票人數比想像中高，相信源於政制局局長曾國衞恐嚇初選或違反國安法，及警員闖入香港民研辦公室，令港人反感。另一超區參選人為元朗區議員王百羽。"},{"pid":"ee4f4f9005ee2ba89a8ecde46cc94e7914518d06","tid":2104442,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"未投既 請今日去投，<br />\n<br />\n投咗既 請盡量去票站睇下有咩幫到手。<br />\n<br />\n0900-2100<br />\n<br />\nGo go go go go"}]}